/**
 * Memory Search Bar Component
 *
 * Powerful search toolbar for finding memories in the Vault with Cmd+K shortcut.
 * Features:
 * - Cmd+K/Ctrl+K keyboard shortcut
 * - Debounced real-time search (300ms)
 * - Arrow key navigation
 * - Memory type icons and metadata display
 * - Tag filtering and display
 * - Loading and error states
 * - Keyboard accessible
 *
